description: Your childhood dreams have finally come true with the emergence of NeatMeat, the D.C. area's premiere spot for sloppy joes! They've turned this classic treat into a gourmet delicacy with menu items including traditional beef joes as well as never seen options including turkey, lamb, pork and even a vegan joe. Enjoy your sloppy joe with chips, a cool sweet tea, and a mouthwatering Joe Crispy bar dessert and you'll be in heaven!
name: Neat Meat DC
